        "TileImage": "$($repository 73e78ce3-4612-4fc0-8c6b-1b57ad9a5ef0).Image",
        "Description": "Good Day 47,\rThe Three Leaf Clover has hidden its corruption behind charm, tradition, and a polished green veneer. Today, five of its members move through the St. Patrick’s Day crowd, disguised in green and shielded by false celebration. Their luck has finally run out.\rIdentify each target and strip this organization of every last leaf.\r\rGood Luck.\r\rBy - SW",
